ilians%20in%20occupied%20regions%2C%20including%20Kherson%20and%20Bucha.%3Cp%3EThough%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20are%20the%20most%20frequent%20targets%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20Russians%20use%20rape%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20tactic%26quot%3B%20to%20dehumanize%20victims%20regardless%20of%20sex%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-soldiers-supplied-with-viagra-to-rape-ukrainians-un-official-2022-10%5C%22%3EInsider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20women%20are%20held%20for%20days%20and%20raped%2C%20when%20you%20start%20to%20rape%20little%20boys%20and%20men%2C%20when%20you%20see%20a%20series%20of%20genital%20mutilations%2C%20when%20you%20hear%20women%20testify%20about%20Russian%20soldiers%20equipped%20with%20Viagra%2C%20it's%20clearly%20a%20military%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20Pramila%20Patten%2C%20the%20UN's%20special%20representative%20on%20sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict%2C%20told%20AFP%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22c84c0d45e3fbf0f501dc9418423f6a86%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20221014-rape-used-in-ukraine-as-a-russian-military-strategy-un%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20France%2024.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERape%20as%20a%20weapon%20of%20war%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20rapes%20are%20no%20doubt%20troubling%2C%20sexual%20violence%20is%20frequently%20documented%20during%20wartime.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icc-cpi.int%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FRS-Eng.pdf%5C%22%3EThe%20Rome%20Statute%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20classifies%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-officers-used-female-medics-as-sex-slaves-solider-says-2023-3%5C%22%3Esexual%20slavery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20forced%20prostitution%2C%20and%20sterilization%2C%20as%20a%20type%20of%20war%20crime%20and%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20context%20under%20which%20the%20crimes%20are%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRape%20committed%20during%20war%20is%20often%20intended%20to%20terrorize%20the%20population%2C%20break%20up%20families%2C%20destroy%20communities%2C%20and%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20change%20the%20ethnic%20make-up%20of%20the%20next%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20a%202014%20UN%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fpreventgenocide%2Frwanda%2Fassets%2Fpdf%2FBackgrounder%2520Sexual%2520Violence%25202014.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20sexual%20violence%20during%20war%2C%20which%20highlighted%20sexual%20violence%20during%20the%20Rwandan%20genocide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20100%2C000%20and%20250%2C000%20women%20were%20raped%20over%20three%20months%20in%201994%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20At%20least%20200%2C000%20women%20were%20raped%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%20since%201998%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20more%20during%20wars%20in%20Sierra%20Leone%2C%20Liberia%2C%20and%20the%20former%20Yugoslavia%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20it%20is%20also%20used%20to%20deliberately%20infect%20women%20with%20HIV%20or%20render%20women%20from%20the%20targeted%20community%20incapable%20of%20bearing%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%202014%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20international%20law%20provides%20protections%20against%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20enforcement%20of%20the%20provisions%20is%20weak%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkglobalhealth.org%2Farticle%2Fdevastating-use-sexual-violence-weapon-war%5C%22%3ECouncil%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20think%20tank.%20The%20International%20Crime%20Court%20has%20launched%20an%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20war%20crimes%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20though%20legal%20action%20is%20unlikely%20to%20come%20for%20many%20years%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20comes%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternational%20law%20is%20largely%20ineffective%20at%20preventing%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20which%20advocates%20for%20a%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20helping%20survivors%2C%20rather%20than%20focusing%20on%20the%20near-impossible%20task%20of%20ending%20sexual%20violence%20during%20wartime.%20%26quot%3BSurvivor-centered%20training%20and%20aid%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20support%20victims%20of%20sexual%20violence%20and%20to%20help%20them%20cope%20with%20the%20trauma%2C%20stigma%2C%20and%20the%20health%20consequences%20stemming%20from%20conflict-related%20sexual%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-troops-rape-ukrainian-women-force-families-listen-war-crime-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695685776000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511fdcc59fd710019f013f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-troops-rape-ukrainian-women-force-families-listen-war-crime-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20report%20from%20the%20UN%20found%20evidence%20that%20women%20in%20the%20Kherson%20region%20of%20Ukraine%20have%20been%20victims%20of%20systematic%20sexual%20violence%20by%20Russian%20troops.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-troops-rape-ukrainian-women-force-families-listen-war-crime-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20stops%20by%20a%20gu