ages%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2F2023-196%3Futm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20SEC%20charged%3C%2Fa%3E%20Matthew%20Motil%20for%20fraudulently%20raising%20%2411%20million%20in%20a%20Ponzi%20scheme.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EMotil%2C%20the%20host%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Cash%20Flow%20King%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20roped%20in%20more%20than%2050%20investors%2C%20the%20SEC%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20complaint%20said%20Motil%20invited%20potential%20investors%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20a%20real%20estate%20investing%20badass!%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20on%20Monday%20announced%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-release%2F2023-196%3Futm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Dgovdelivery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20had%20charged%3C%2Fa%3E%20Matthew%20Motil%2C%20the%20host%20of%20the%20podcast%20%26quot%3BThe%20Cash%20Flow%20King%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20running%20a%20real%20estate%20Ponzi%20scheme%20that%20raised%20roughly%20%2411%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SEC's%20complaint%2C%20which%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20US%20District%20Court%20for%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20Ohio%2C%20charges%20Motil%20with%20%26quot%3Bviolating%20the%20registration%20and%20antifraud%20provisions%20of%20the%20Securities%20Act%20of%201933%20and%20the%20antifraud%20provisions%20of%20the%20Securities%20Exchange%20Act%20of%201934.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20podcast%20host%20used%20the%20funds%20taken%20from%20investors%20to%20pay%20back%20previous%20investors%20in%20the%20scheme%2C%20but%20also%20to%20finance%20a%20lavish%20lifestyle%2C%20which%20the%20SEC%20says%20included%20a%20lakeside%20mansion%2C%20courtside%20tickets%20to%20NBA%20games%2C%20and%20%24400%2C000%20of%20credit%20card%20payments%20for%20Motil's%20wife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMotil%20fraudulently%20raised%20the%20money%20from%20more%20than%2050%20investors%2C%20leveraging%20social%20media%20to%20promote%20notes%20that%20were%20purportedly%20backed%20by%20residential%20properties%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%20Motil%20attempted%20to%20convince%20investors%20with%20promises%20of%20low-risk%2C%20high-return%20promissory%20notes%20that%20were%20collateralized%20by%20first%20mortgages%20on%20homes%20in%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20complaint%20alleges%2C%20however%2C%20Motil%20did%20not%20in%20fact%20secure%20first%20lien%20positions%20for%20the%20investors%20as%20promised%20and%20regularly%20sold%20multiple%20promissory%20notes%20he%20claimed%20were%20secured%20by%20the%20same%20property%20to%20multiple%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SEC's%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20one%20instance%2C%20Motil%20allegedly%20sold%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20of%20promissory%20notes%20to%2020%20investors%2C%20each%20note%20supposedly%20collateralized%20by%20the%20same%20property%20he%20had%20acquired%20for%20%2447%2C000.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20his%20podcast%2C%20website%2C%20and%20social%20media%20channels%2C%20Motil%20invited%20potential%20participants%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20a%20real%20estate%20investing%20badass!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20allege%20that%20Motil%20used%20podcasts%20and%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20bolster%20his%20reputation%20as%20an%20investing%20expert%20while%20fraudulently%20targeting%20investors'%20hard-earned%20retirement%20assets%2C%20including%2C%20in%20at%20least%20one%20instance%2C%20almost%20the%20full%20balance%20of%20an%20investor's%20self-directed%20IRA%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Cave%2C%20associate%20director%20of%20the%20Division%20of%20Enforcement%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20holding%20those%20who%20prey%20on%20others%20accountable%20for%20their%20unlawful%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20podcaster%20also%20communicated%20that%20he%20would%20pay%20the%20investor%20returns%20on%20investment%20profits%20that%20came%20from%20renovating%2C%20reselling%2C%20renting%2C%20and%20refinancing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20complaint%20seeks%20injunctive%20relief%2C%20disgorgement%20plus%20prejudgment%20interest%2C%20civil%20money%20penalties%2C%20and%20an%20officer%20and%20director%20bar%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20SEC%20statement%20reads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsec-ponzi-scheme-cash-flow-king-podcast-mansion-nba-courtside-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695669139000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511da7459fd710019f00b2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsec-ponzi-scheme-cash-flow-king-podcast-mansion-nba-courtside-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Matthew%20Motil%2C%20the%20host%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Cash%20Flow%20King%26quot%3B%20used%20social%20media%20to%20lure%20more%20than%2050%20investors%20into%20a%20real%20estate%20fraud%20scheme%2C%20the%20SEC%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22prosen%40insider.com%20(Phil%20Rosen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsec-ponzi-scheme-cash-flow-king-podcast-mansion-nba-courtside-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Saturday%20Night%20Live%E2%80%99%20Could%20Return%20in%20October%20As%20Writers%20Await%20WGA%20Greenlight%20to%20Return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695668460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNUP_201339_00048.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235734497%22