ns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0company%20plans%20to%20conduct%20trials%20on%20patients%20with%20anodontia%2C%20a%20congenital%20condition%20in%20which%20some%20or%20all%20permanent%20teeth%20are%20absent.%C2%A0The%20children%20will%20be%20injected%20with%20one%20dose%20to%20induce%20teeth%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMissing%20teeth%20in%20a%20child%20can%20affect%20the%20development%20of%20their%20jaw%20bone.%20We%20hope%20the%20drug%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20key%20to%20solving%20those%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Katsu%20Takahashi%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Toregem%20Biopharma%20and%20head%20of%20dentistry%20and%20oral%20surgery%20at%20Kitano%20Hospital%20in%20Osaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20also%20hoping%20to%20utilize%20the%20drug%20in%20the%20future%20for%20adults%20who%20have%20lost%20teeth%20due%20to%20cavities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToregem's%20president%20Honoka%20Kiso%20wrote%20on%20the%20company's%20website%20she%20had%20lost%20teeth%20due%20to%20a%20bone%20disease%20when%20she%20was%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20study%20the%20cause%20of%20my%20illness%20and%20how%20to%20regenerate%20lost%20teeth.%C2%A0Toregem%20Biopharma%20first%20hopes%20to%20treat%20patients%20with%20congenital%20tooth%20loss%20who%20do%20not%20grow%20permanent%20tooth%20buds%20due%20to%20genetic%20causes.%20Our%20final%20goal%20is%20to%20offer%20advanced%20and%20scientifically%20driven%20clinical%20solutions%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20teeth%20derived%20from%20their%20own%20tissues%2C''%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695666000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ft8v2vr1o_teeth_625x300_25_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthis-japanese-company-is-working-on-worlds-first-drug-to-grow-new-teeth-4423433%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20is%20set%20to%20conduct%20clinical%20trials%20on%20healthy%20adults%20in%20July%20