0BJP%20workers%20in%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgriculture%20Minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Dimani%2C%20Prahlad%20Patel%20(Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Food%20Processing%20Industries%20and%20Jal%20Shakti)%20from%20Narsingpur%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20(Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Rural%20Development%20and%20Steel)%20from%20Niwas%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Tomar%20will%20contest%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20after%20two%20decades.%20He%20last%20won%20the%20assembly%20polls%20from%20Gwalior%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20a%20row%20in%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20the%20name%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20national%20general%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%20has%20also%20been%20included%20in%20the%20list%2C%20a%20decade%20after%20he%20won%20the%20Mhow%20seat%20of%20native%20Indore%20district%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%202013.%20He%20will%20contest%20from%20Indore-1%20seat.%20His%20inclusion%20has%20ended%20any%20possibility%20of%20his%20son%20Akash%20getting%20a%20ticket.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20central%20leadership%20is%20upset%20with%20Akash%20over%20a%202019%20incident%20when%20he%20attacked%20a%20civic%20body%20official%20in%20Indore%20with%20a%20cricket%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFour%20Lok%20Sabha%20members%20have%20also%20featured%20in%20the%20list.%20Four-time%20MP%20from%20Satna%20seat%20Ganesh%20Singh%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20his%20current%20seat%2C%20second-time%20sitting%20MP%20Riti%20Pathak%20from%20Sidhi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20been%20given%20ticker%20for%20Sishi%20assembly%20seat%2C%20four-time%20Jabalpur%20MP%20Rakesh%20Singh%20will%20contest%20from%20Jabalpur-West%20and%20third%20time%20MP%20from%20Hoshangabad%20seat%20Uday%20Pratap%20Singh%20will%20be%20in%20the%20fray%20from%20Gadarwara%20seat%20of%20Narsinghpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESidhi%20assembly%20seat%20is%20presently%20held%20by%20BJP%20MLA%20Kedarnath%20Shukla.%20It%20is%20being%20speculated%20that%20he%20is%20being%20denied%20the%20ticket%20over%20his%20alleged%20supporter%20Pravesh%20Shukla's%20video%20of%20urinating%20on%20a%20tribal%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20might%20use%20the%20same%20formula%20of%20naming%20Union%20Ministers%20and%20MPs%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan%20-%20both%20ruled%20by%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%20too%2C%20Union%20Minister%20G%20Kishan%20Reddy%20might%20contest%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImarti%20Devi%2C%20a%20loyalist%20of%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20-%20whose%202020%20coup%20had%20toppled%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20-%C2%A0%20has%20also%20figured%20in%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20first%20list%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20also%20had%2039%20candidates%20for%20the%20election%20to%20the%20230-member%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20is%20one%20of%20five%20states%2C%20along%20with%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram%2C%20which%20are%20scheduled%20to%20go%20to%20poll%20later%20this%20year.%20Only%20one%20of%20these%20states%20has%20a%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20in%202018%2C%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%20and%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20senior%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20formed%20the%20government%20in%202020%20after%20then%20Congress%20leader%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20along%20with%2022%20MLAs%2C%20switched%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695663780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F41prtftg_bjp-generic_625x300_07_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-union-ministers-in-bjps-second-list-of-39-candidates-for-madhya-pradesh-polls-4423004%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20Union%20Ministers%20-%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20-%20have%20made%20it%20to%20the%20BJP's%20second%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-union-ministers-in-bjps-second-list-of-39-candidates-for-madhya-pradesh-polls-4423004%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-union-ministers-in-bjps-second-list-of-39-candidates-for-madhya-pradesh-polls-4423004%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F3-union-ministers-in-bjps-second-list-of-39-candidates-for-madhya-pradesh-polls-4423004%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Journalist%20Unions%20Send%20Legal%20Notices%20To%20Editors%20Guild%20Over%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManipur's%20journalists'%20union%20and%20the%20state's%20editors%20guild%20have%20sent%20legal%20notices%20to%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20(EGI)%20over%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bbiased%20and%20sponsored%26quot%3B%20information%20%26quot%3Bfavouring%20one%20particular%20community%20only%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20EGI's%20report%20on%20the%20media%20coverage%20of%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20published%20on%20September%204%20by%20a%20three-member%2C%20crowdfunded%20EGI%20team%20after%20staying%20in%20Manipur%20for%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20notices%20to%20the%20EGI%20sent%20by%20the%20All%20Manipur%20Working%20Journalists%20Union%20(AMWJU)%20and%20the%20Editors'%20Guild%20of%20Manipur%20(EGM)%20said%20the%20EGI's%20report%20led%20to%20escalation%20of%20violence%20when%20Manipur%20was%20limping%20back%20to%20normalcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20apex%20body%20of%20editors%20like%20the%20EGI%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20while%20publishing%20its%20report%20on%20a%20sensitive%20issue%20like%20that%20of%20Manipur...%20The%20so-called%20report%20only%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20that%20has%20been%20burning%20in%20Manipur%20for%20more%20than%20four%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notices%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20not%20only%20escalated%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur...%20but%20spread%20false%20news%2C%20which%20were%20ill%20motivated%2C%20biased%2C%20sponsored%20and%20fabricated...%20favouring%20one%20particular%20community%20only%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20completely%20violating%20the%20ethics%20of%20journalism%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AMWJU%20and%20the%20EGM%20said%20in%20the%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20cited%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanufactured-report-manipurs-top-forest-official-slams-editors-guild-of-india-4372530%5C%22%3EManipur%20Forest%20Department's%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20state%20government%20denying%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20EGI's%20fact-finding%20team%20on%20the%20status%20of%20%26quot%3Breserved%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bprotected%26quot%3B%20forests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrincipal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%20SS%20Chhabra%20in%20a%20seven-page%20letter%20to%20the%20Manipur%20government%20on%20September%208%20had%20said%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20forest%20department%20in%20the%20report%20were%20%26quot%3Bwrong%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunverified%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20they%20have%20%26quot%3Bled%20to%20misinformation...%20and%20tarnished%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20forest%20department.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%2C%20the%20EGI%20alleged%20there%20are%20clear%20indications%20that%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20state%20became%20partisan%20during%20the%20conflict.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20have%20avoided%20taking%20sides%20in%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20but%20it%20failed%20to%20do%20its%20duty%20as%20a%20democratic%20government%20which%20should%20have%20repres