2content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Criminal%20Police%20Organization%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20Interpol%2C%20on%20Monday%20issued%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20against%20Karanvir%20Singh%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20banned%20terrorist%20group%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterpol%20updated%20its%20website%20by%20putting%20out%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20for%20the%20Khalistani%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20hiding%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20pro-Khalistan%20terrorist%20group%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%2C%20intelligence%20sources%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Interpol%20portal%2C%2038-year-old%20Karanvir%20Singh%20has%20roots%20in%20Punjab's%20Kapurthala%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20according%20to%20Interpol%2C%20Singh%20is%20wanted%20by%20India%20for%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20murder%2C%20offences%20related%20to%20the%20Arms%20Act%2C%20and%20Explosive%20Substances%20Act%2C%20raising%20funds%20for%20terrorist%20acts%2C%20conspiracy%2C%20and%20being%20a%20member%20of%20a%20terrorist%20gang%20or%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20is%20a%20request%20to%20the%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20of%20Interpol's%20member%20countries%20to%20find%20and%20temporarily%20detain%20a%20person%20until%20extradition%2C%20surrender%2C%20or%20a%20similar%20legal%20process%20can%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Interpol%20issued%20a%20Red%20Notice%20to%20all%20member%20countries%20against%20gangster%20Himanshu%20alias%20Bhau%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20living%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiving%20details%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20of%20Haryana%20Police%20said%20Rohtak%20Police%20succeeded%20in%20getting%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20issued%20against%20a%20most%20wanted%20accused%2C%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20fled%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20against%20the%20wanted%20pro-Khalistani%20terrorist%20comes%20amid%20a%20diplomatic%20spat%20between%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20claim%20of%20an%20India%20hand%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%2C%20calling%20them%20'absurd'%20and%20'motivated'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20news%20conference%20in%20New%20York%2C%20the%20Canadian%20PM%2C%20however%2C%20failed%20to%20present%20any%20evidence%20to%20back%20his%20claim%20of%20Indian%20involvement%20in%20Nijjar's%20killing.%20Trudeau%20was%20repeatedly%20quizzed%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20allegations%20but%20stuck%20to%20reiterating%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20reasons%26quot%3B%20to%20believe%20that%20India%20was%20linked%20to%20Nijjar's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20credible%20reasons%20to%20believe%20that%20agents%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20Canadian%20on%20Canadian%20soil.%20That%20is%20...there%20is%20something%20of%20utmost%20foundational%20importance%20in%20a%20country's%20rule%20of%20law%20in%20a%20world%20where%20international%20rules-based%20order%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20call%20upon%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20take%20seriously%20this%20matter%20and%20to%20work%20with%20us%20to%20shed%20full%20transparency%20and%20ensure%20accountability%20and%20justice%20in%20this%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Canadian%20PM%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CBC%20News%2C%20the%20Canadian%20government%20invested%20both%20human%20and%20signal%20intelligence%20in%20a%20months-long%20investigation%20into%20Nijjar's%20death.%20That%20intelligence%20includes%20communications%20involving%20Indian%20diplomats%20present%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20on%20Thursday%2C%20however%2C%20said%20no%20information%20has%20been%20shared%20by%20Canada%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20willing%20to%20look%20at%20any%20specific%20information%20that%20is%20provided%20to%20us%2C%20but%20so%20far%20we%20have%20received%20no%20specific%20information%20from%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20Arindam%20Bagchi%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%2C%20said%20during%20a%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20designated%20terrorist%20in%20India%2C%20Nijjar%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20on%20June%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695661380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fu5nq8u74_karanvir-singh-1200_625x300_25_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterpol-issues-red-corner-notice-against-wanted-khalistani-terrorist-karanvir-singh-4423286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Criminal%20Police%20Organization%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20Interpol%2C%20on%20Monday%20issued%20a%20Red%20Corner%20Notice%20against%20Karanvir%20Singh%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20banned%20terrorist%20group%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterpol-issues-red-corner-notice-against-wanted-khalistani-terrorist-karanvir-singh-4423286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterpol-issues-red-corner-notice-against-wanted-khalistani-terrorist-karanvir-singh-4423286%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterp