%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22095913%2FF6ga_ibawAAlDWp-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674218%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20Manipur%20Police%20checkpoint.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40manipur_police%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20which%20is%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20only%20neutral%20force%20is%20operating%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20state%20security%20apparatus.%20But%20perhaps%20what%20rankles%20the%20most%20for%20all%20those%20who%20have%20watched%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20descent%20to%20chaos%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20man%20holding%20the%20reins%20of%20governance%20and%20failing%20miserably%20to%20do%20so%20is%20still%20presiding%20over%20the%20chaos%20and%20loss%20of%20over%20170%20human%20lives%20and%20the%20displacement%20of%2C%20at%20least%2C%20about%2070%2C000%20people%20from%20their%20hearths%20and%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20state%20within%20a%20federal%20republic%20is%20unable%20to%20put%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20killing%20and%20mayhem%20for%20143%20days%20(as%20of%20writing%20this%20article)%2C%20the%20correct%20thing%20to%20do%20is%20to%20remove%20him%20and%20bring%20in%20central%20rule.%20This%20would%20at%20least%20be%20seen%20by%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20heal%20their%20wounds.%20But%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20been%20indulging%20in%20some%20sort%20of%20talks%20with%20different%20groups%20in%20Delhi.%20These%20talks%20obviously%20are%20not%20reaching%20anywhere%20because%20what%20leaders%20from%20both%20communities%20speak%20inside%20closed%20doors%20cannot%20be%20shared.%20Once%20outside%2C%20the%20negotiators%20have%20to%20adopt%20the%20correct%20posturing%20to%20convey%20to%20their%20people%20that%20they%20have%20not%20given%20in%2C%20nor%20given%20away%20an%20inch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoints%20of%20conflict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20bleak%20scenario%2C%20perhaps%2C%20the%20only%20institution%20that%20can%20bring%20in%20a%20semblance%20of%20order%20is%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20There%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20committee%20with%20a%20timeline%20to%20study%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(a)%20The%20inherent%20and%20legacy%20problems%20around%20land%2C%20and%20a%20clear%20declaration%20from%20the%20Geological%20Survey%20of%20India%20as%20to%20the%20mineral%20resources%20detected%20in%20the%20Hills%20of%20Manipur.%20This%20transparency%20is%20critical%20in%20order%20to%20put%20the%20lid%20on%20all%20kinds%20of%20wild%20assumptions%20that%20fuel%20fear%20in%20one%20of%20the%20groups%20and%20opportunism%20in%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(b)%20The%20narcotics%20trade%2C%20normally%20controlled%20by%20militant%20outfits%2C%20is%20a%20smoke-and-mirrors%20issue.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20there%20are%20only%20allegations%20and%20counter-allegations%20as%20to%20who%20is%20actually%20knee-deep%20in%20this%20multi-crore%20trade.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20clarity%20on%20this%3F%20Who%20are%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20drug%20trade%3F%20Here%20too%2C%20we%20need%20a%20completely%20independent%20inquiry.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20not%20forget%20that%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%2050%20kilograms%20of%20opium%20valued%20at%20Rs%2010%20crore%20was%20seized%20from%20the%20secret%20cavities%20of%20a%20vehicle.%20The%20supplier%2C%20Loyangamba%20Itocha%2C%20a%20Meitei%2C%20and%20Ranbir%20Singh%2C%20the%20buyer%2C%20were%20both%20arrested%20near%20the%20Badarpur%20border.%20This%20calls%20out%20the%20lie%20that%20only%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20narcotics%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20state%20is%20concerned%2C%20since%20the%20issue%20of%20land%20is%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20there%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20a%20cadastral%20survey%20to%20get%20a%20grip%20on%20who%20actually%20holds%20how%20much%20land%20in%20Manipur.%20In%20a%20country%20governed%20by%20a%20robust%20constitution%2C%20and%20with%20protective%20clauses%20like%20Article%20371%20C%2C%20to%20protect%20tribal%20interests%2C%20can%20we%20have%20parallel%20ancestral%20land-holding%20systems%20without%20any%20land%20reforms%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Kukis%20follow%20two%20distinct%20land%20ownership%20practices%3A%20the%20traditional%20and%20the%20modern%20chieftainship.%20In%20the%20traditional%20system%2C%20the%20chief%20who%20usually%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20clan%20(eldest%20male%20in%20the%20family%20lineage)%20owns%20the%20whole%20land%20in%20his%20name.%20Apart%20from%20his%20own%20kinsmen%2C%20he%20may%20allow%20kinsmen%20who%20are%20not%20of%20his%20lineage%20or%20even%20other%20clans%20to%20settle%20in%20his%20jurisdiction%20but%20legal%20ownership%20is%20in%20his%20name.%20He%20may%20transfer%20the%20land%20to%20his%20younger%20brothers%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20village%2C%20but%20that%20village%20will%20bear%20the%20initials%20of%20the%20parent%20village%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20modern%20chieftain%20system%2C%20the%20chief%20allows%20all%20the%20villagers%20to%20have%20legal%20land%20ownership%20documents%20by%20giving%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20so%20that%20the%20patch%20of%20land%20is%20registered%20separately%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20occupant%2Fowner%20within%20the%20village%20jurisdiction.%20One%20reason%20why%20the%20affluent%20Kukis%20want%20to%20settle%20in%20Imphal%20is%20due%20to%20the%20autocratic%20traditional%20system%20of%20land%20ownership%20where%20the%20villagers%20live%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20chief%20at%20all%20times.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20Nagas%20and%20Mizos%20have%20abolished%20the%20traditional%20chieftainship%20system%20and%20the%20land%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20community%20and%20state%20respectively.%20This%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20have%20to%20resolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocal%20power%20dynamics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInequity%20is%20the%20breeding%20ground%20for%20conflicts.%20How%20are%20the%20power%20dynamics%20in%20Manipur%3F%20Who%20calls%20the%20shots%3F%20Who%20is%20controlling%20the%20narrative%20and%20the%20police%20and%20administration%20today%3F%20It%20is%20naturally%20the%20Meiteis%20since%20they%20now%20have%20complete%20control%20over%20Imphal%20Valley.%20It%20has%20been%20purged%20of%20all%20Kuki-Zo%20tribals.%20Recently%2C%20a%20soldier%20from%20the%20Kom%20(Naga)%20community%20living%20in%20Imphal%20was%20mercilessly%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11194911%2FF0ubs4CWcAEONzp.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11194911%2FF0ubs4CWcAEONzp.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11194911%2FF0ubs4CWcAEONzp-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11194911%2FF0ubs4CWcAEONzp-1024x681.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662710%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EManipur%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40NBirenSingh%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20is%20non-existent%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20does%20not%20feel%20safe%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20hills%20how%20can%20anyone%20speak%20of%20bringing%20peace%3F%20Chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20lost%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20groups.%20His%20continuance%20in%20office%20is%20a%20sore%20point%20for%20them.%20Every%20action%20of%20the%20state%20government%20today%20is%20viewed%20with%20suspicion%2C%20especially%20after%20senior%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officers%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20have%20been%20arbitrarily%20removed%20from%20their%20former%20positions%20and%20given%20insignificant%20postings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20sizeable%20presence%20of%20Kuki%20officers%20in%20the%20Manipur%20administration.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20join%20their%20services%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20lynched%20if%20they%20come%20to%20Imphal%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20directed%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20go%20into%20the%20various%20human%20rights%20violations%20and%20sexual%20abuses%2C%20but%20even%20here%20a%20fair%20and%20impartial%20investigation%20is%20impossible%20due%20to%20interference%20by%20different%20Valley-based%20groups.%20Recently%2C%20five%20youths%20dressed%20in%20camouflage%20and%20moving%20around%20with%20arms%20impersonating%20the%20special%20forces%20were%20arrested%2C%20and%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20(women%20vigilante)%20called%20a%2048-hour%20bandh%20and%20resorted%20to%20other%20shenanigans%20to%20demand%20their%20release.%20Where%20is%20the%20state%20in%20such%20a%20situation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-tribal-politics-behind-manipur-conflict%5C%22%3EThe%20Tribal%20Politics%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Conflict%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20palpable%20inequity%20even%20in%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20displaced%20persons.%20Meiteis%20displaced%20from%20Chandel%20and%20other%20districts%20were%20provided%20housing%20in%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20in%20Imphal.%20No%20such%20efforts%20were%20made%20to%20rehabilitate%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20groups%20which%20are%20displaced%20by%20the%20thousands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20all%20accounts%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20two%20communities%20have%20reached%20a%20point%20of%20no%20return.%20The%20Nagas%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20joined%20forces%20with%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20opposing%20any%20settlement%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zos.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20case%20of%20my%20enemy%E2%80%99s%20enemy%20is%20my%20friend.%20But%20this%20bonhomie%20might%20last%20until%20the%20Naga%20Framework%20Agreement%20takes%20effect%20and%20new%20boundary%20lines%20are%20drawn.%20This%20will%20lead%20to%20another%20outburst%20of%20dissension.%20Manipur%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20a%20cauldron%20that%20will%20continue%20to%20brew%20poison.%20It%20would%20take%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20statesmanship%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20situation.%20Politicians%20are%20the%20cause%20of%20all%20dissensions.%20Looking%20to%20them%20to%20resolve%20conflicts%20%E2%80%93%20which%20they%20are%20largely%20responsible%20for%20igniting%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20is%20a%20fool%E2%80%99s%20errand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%E2%80%99s%20the%20point%20in%20having%20over%2040%2C000%20boots%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20are%20essentially%20sent%20to%20Manipur%20with%20their%20hands%20tied%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-win%20situation%20anyway%20as%20we%20look%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPatricia%20Mukhim%20is%20the%20editor%20of%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Shillong%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A169566125