icket%20World%20Cup%3A%20India%20Grants%20Visas%20to%20Pakistan%20Players%20After%20PCB%20Petitions%20ICC%20Over%20Delay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25203144%2FThe-Wire-19.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20India%20granting%20visas%20to%20its%20players%2C%20the%20host%20country%20issued%20visas%20to%20the%20cricket%20team%20from%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVisas%20have%20been%20issued%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20ICC%20spokesperson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fvisas-issued-pakistan-team-world-cup-india-2023-09-25%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNEW%2520DELHI%252C%2520Sept%252025%2520(Reuters%2Ca%2520delay%2520in%2520the%2520process%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Reuters%20without%20sharing%20any%20further%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPCB%20spokesperson%20Umar%20Farooq%20also%20confirmed%20to%20Reuters%20that%20players%20and%20support%20staff%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20collect%20their%20passports%20from%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20had%20written%20to%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%2C%20raising%20concerns%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20getting%20visas%20for%20its%20team%20members%20who%20will%20play%20in%20the%20upcoming%20World%20Cup%20hosted%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20PCB%E2%80%99s%20schedule%2C%20the%20team%20was%20supposed%20to%20travel%20to%20Hyderabad%20from%20Dubai%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2027%2C%20to%20play%20a%20warm-up%20match%20with%20New%20Zeland%20on%20September%2029%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20before%20the%20actual%20tournament%20begins%20on%20October%205.%20With%20just%20two%20days%20left%20before%20their%20departure%2C%20the%20team%20members%20were%20still%20waiting%20to%20get%20their%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20last%20week%20PCB%20is%20being%20informed%20that%20the%20visas%20will%20be%20received%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20but%20still%20awaiting%20and%20it%20has%20been%20indicated%20that%20the%20Indian%20home%20ministry%20has%20not%20granted%20NOC%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20PCB%20spokesperson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-2023-no-visa-for-pakistan-yet-pcb-writes-to-icc-report-4422212%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20PTI%20on%20Monday%2C%20September%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20an%20extraordinary%20delay%20in%20getting%20clearance%20and%20securing%20Indian%20visas%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20for%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20PCB%20spokesperson%20Umar%20Farooq%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fworld-cup-pakistan-squad-yet-to-get-their-visas-less-than-48-hours-before-flying-out-to-india-1399966%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EESPNCricinfo%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20written%20to%20ICC%20raising%20our%20concerns%20about%20inequitable%20treatment%20towards%20Pakistan%20and%20reminding%20them%20of%20these%20obligations%20towards%20the%20World%20Cup.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVisa%20applications%20from%20Pakistan%20require%20clearances%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20external%20affairs%2C%20and%20sports%20ministries.%20India%E2%80%99s%20high%20commission%20in%20Islamabad%20was%20still%20awaiting%20clearance%20from%20the%20authorities%20to%20issue%20visas%20to%20the%20Pakistani%20contingent.%20The%20entire%20schedule%20drawn%20up%20by%20the%20PCB%20earlier%20for%20its%20team%20and%20support%20staff%20had%20to%20be%20reworked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20team%20and%20its%20support%20staff%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20in%20Dubai%20for%20a%20two-day%20team%20bonding%20session%20before%20flying%20from%20there%20to%20Hyderabad%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2027%20morning.%20However%2C%20the%20Dubai%20team-bonding%20session%20had%20to%20be%20cancelled%2C%20and%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20team%20would%20directly%20fly%20out%20of%20Lahore%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%20to%20reach%20Hyderabad%20subject%20to%20visa%20clearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20of%20disappointment%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20has%20to%20go%20through%20this%20uncertainty%20ahead%20of%20the%20major%20tournament.%20We%20have%20been%20reminding%20%5Bthe%20organisers%5D%20about%20their%20obligations%20from%20the%20last%20three%20years%20and%20it%20has%20all%20come%20down%20to%20the%20last%20two%20days%20with%20our%20first%20warm%20game%20scheduled%20on%20September%2029.%20We%20were%20forced%20to%20cancel%20our%20original%20plan%20to%20organise%20team-building%20exercises%20in%20Dubai%20on%20the%20way%20to%20India.%20We%20have%20had%20to%20rework%20our%20plan%20and%20book%20new%20flights%2C%20but%20these%20plans%20are%20subject%20to%20issuance%20of%20visas%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PCB%20had%20told%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20last%20visited%20India%20in%202016%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20The%20arch-rivals%20only%20play%20with%20each%20other%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20ICC%20tournaments%20given%20the%20hostile%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20players%20are%20having%20to%20experience%20delays%2C%20one%20can%20only%20wonder%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20visa%20applications%20of%20fans%20and%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20PCB%20source%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20copy%20has%20been%20updated%20with%20the%20news%20of%20India%20granting%20visas%20to%20Pakistan%20players%20after%20it%20was%20published.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695654270000%2C%22visua