ttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25164355%2Fimage-1352.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20printer%20who%20worked%20closely%20with%20my%20husband%20for%20many%20years%20and%20became%20a%20family%20friend%20once%20phoned%20when%20he%20found%20out%20Dev%20Anand%20was%20in%20London%20to%20launch%20his%20autobiography.%20Ajay%20had%20never%20asked%20us%20for%20a%20favour%20but%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20there%20was%20any%20way%20we%20could%20introduce%20him%20to%20Dev%20Anand.%20We%20not%20only%20met%20him%20but%20even%20joined%20him%20for%20dinner.%20A%20truly%20memorable%20experience%20for%20Ajay%20and%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20was%20privileged%20to%20meet%20Dev%20Anand%20several%20times%20in%20India%20and%20in%20London.%20I%20was%20always%20charmed%20and%20delighted%20by%20this%20iconic%20star%20and%20perfect%20gentleman%20while%20he%20was%20amused%20to%20meet%20a%20foreigner%20who%20was%20his%20fan%20and%20knew%20his%20oeuvre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20was%20puzzled.%20Why%20is%20Ajay%20such%20a%20fan%20of%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20who%20was%20older%20than%20his%20parents%20rather%20than%20of%20the%20stars%20of%20the%2080s%2F90s%3F%20This%20might%20be%20explained%20by%20personal%20reasons%20but%20I%20believe%20it%20was%20not%20just%20that%20Dev%20Anand%20was%20stylish%20and%20elegant%20or%20a%20good%20actor%20or%20that%20he%20starred%20in%20great%20films%20with%20memorable%20songs%20but%20also%20about%20his%20being%20the%20modern%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDev%20Anand%20was%20a%20mobile%2C%20modern%20Indian%20who%20felt%20equally%20at%20ease%20in%20India%20and%20overseas.%20He%20was%20able%20to%20move%20around%20the%20modern%20city%2C%20Bombay%20(now%20Mumbai)%2C%20interacting%20with%20people%20from%20all%20levels%20of%20society.%20He%20was%20eloquent%20in%20both%20Hindi%20and%20English.%20These%20are%20the%20same%20reasons%20why%20I%20have%20always%20liked%20Dev%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20to%20rank%20the%20three%20great%20stars%20of%20the%201950s%3A%20Dev%20Anand%2C%20Raj%20Kapoor%20and%20Dilip%20Kumar.%20I%20certainly%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20choose%20among%20the%20three.%20I%20admire%20Raj%20Kapoor%20as%20perhaps%20the%20most%20important%20person%20for%20shaping%20the%20style%20of%20the%20mainstream%20Hindi%20cinema%20while%20the%20latter%20was%20such%20an%20elegant%20actor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20had%20family%20roots%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20what%20became%20the%20border%20in%201947.%20Raj%20Kapoor%20was%20the%20pan-Indian%20hero%2C%20a%20villager%20who%20learnt%20the%20evil%20ways%20of%20the%20city%20to%20fit%20into%20the%20high%20society%2C%20taking%20clothes%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98New%20Bharat%20Laundry%E2%80%99%20to%20look%20the%20part%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqu8ShpSlFX0%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShree%20420%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%201955).%20Dilip%20Kumar%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Etangewala%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNz3Ph-I8YPY%26t%3D6555s%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENaya%20Daur%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%201957%3B%20a%20Mughal%20prince%20%3Cem%3Ein%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3De7hP9UNp0Hw%5C%22%3EMughal-e%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%201960%3B%20or%20a%20bandit%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8aEVMuO3NjU%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGunga%20Jumna%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%201961.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDev%20Anand%20often%20appeared%20as%20himself%20from%20film%20to%20film%2C%20with%20his%20distinctive%20hair%20puff%20and%20stylish%20western%20clothes%20%E2%80%93%20a%20jacket%20and%20a%20pair%20of%20trousers%2C%20often%20with%20an%20insouciantly%20tied%20scarf.%20Although%20the%20look%20was%20often%20similar%2C%20well-suited%20to%20an%20urban%20and%20urbane%20hero%2C%20he%20played%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20roles%20convincingly.%20Despite%20his%20good%20looks%2C%20he%20was%20rarely%20just%20a%20romantic%20star%2C%20often%20having%20an%20edge%20to%20him%20or%20even%20clearly%20negative%20shades%2C%20playing%20complex%20characters%20who%20were%20rarely%20all%20bad%20or%20all%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Raj%20Kapoor%20sang%20and%20danced%20and%20Dilip%20Kumar%20had%20a%20contained%20energy%20in%20his%20movements%2C%20Dev%20Anand%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20dance%2C%20looking%20rather%20ungainly%20when%20he%20had%20to%20move%20and%20was%20much%20better-seated%2C%20sometimes%20at%20a%20piano%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJw4wLVnFJ-E%5C%22%3EKhwab%20ho%20tum%20ya%20koi%20haqeeqat%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ETeen%20Deviyan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%201965%2C%20or%20just%20walking%20along%20the%20Bombay%2FMumbai%20seafront%20in%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgvL3q9o7s0E%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELeke%20pehla%20pehla%20pyar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Cem%3ECID%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%201956.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25164802%2Fimage-1353.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221007%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25164802%2Fimage-1353.png%201007w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25164802%2Fimage-1353-300x142.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-676790%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDev%20Anand%20in%20%E2%80%98Leke%20Pehla%20Pehla%20Pyar%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20movie%2C%20%3Cem%3ECID%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fremembering-dev-anand-ten-evergreen-songs-of-the-debonair-lover-boy%5C%22%3ERemembering%20Dev%20Anand%3A%20Ten%20Evergreen%20Songs%20of%20the%20Debonair%20Lover%20Boy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDev%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20offscreen%20persona%20was%20also%20that%20of%20the%20modern%20Indian%20citizen%20created%20by%20the%20new%20state%20of%20India.%20Born%20Dharamdev%20Pishorimal%20Anand%2C%20he%20has%20written%20his%20autobiography%20and%20his%20life%20is%20well-known.%20Born%20in%20an%20educated%20Punjabi%20Khatri%20family%20in%20Gurdaspur%2C%20he%20had%20moved%20to%20study%20in%20Lahore%20before%20Partition%20where%20he%20studied%20English%20literature.%20(Offscreen%2C%20he%20spoke%20in%20a%20very%20clear%2C%20somewhat%20British%20accent%2C%20in%20his%20stylish%20phrasing.)%20Like%20others%20of%20a%20similar%20background%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Sahnis%20and%20the%20Chopras%2C%20his%20brothers%20were%20also%20part%20of%20his%20cultural%20and%20working%20world%2C%20so%20Bhisham%20and%20Balraj%20Sahni%20or%20B.R.%20and%20Yash%20Chopra%2C%20Dev%20Anand%20was%20shaped%20by%20and%20worked%20with%20Chetan%20Anand%20and%20Vijay%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDev%20Anand%20has%20talked%20about%20his%20romances%2C%20but%20the%20only%20two%20worth%20mentioning%20here%20are%20his%20famous%20romance%20with%20his%20co-star%20Suraiya%20in%20the%20late%201940s%2C%20something%20he%20himself%20talked%20about%2C%20given%20how%20formational%20she%20was%20to%20his%20career.%20They%20were%20said%20to%20have%20split%20because%20her%20grandmother%20refused%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20marry%20a%20Hindu.%20He%20married%20another%20co-star%2C%20Kalpana%20Kartik%20(Mona%20Singha)%2C%20in%201954%2C%20who%20stepped%20back%20from%20her%20career%20after%20marriage.%20She%20remained%20a%20practising%20Christian%2C%20and%20they%20were%20married%20for%20almost%2060%20years%20until%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDev%20Anand%20worked%20in%20over%20100%20films%2C%20starting%20in%20Prabhat%20Studios%20in%201946%2C%20then%20active%20as%20an%20actor%2C%20producer%2C%20director%2C%20and%20writer%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life.%20He%20co-founded%20Navketan%20Films%20with%20Chetan%20Anand%20where%20he%20made%20some%20of%20his%20best%20films.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20aspects%20of%20Dev%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20long%20career%20which%20I%20particularly%20enjoyed%20were%20the%20fruit%20of%20his%20working%20with%20other%20talented%20individuals%2C%20including%20some%20of%20the%20great%20female%20stars%20of%20his%20era%2C%20but%20here%20I%20look%20at%20his%20work%20with%20his%20brothers%20and%20others%20at%20Navketan%20Films%20and%20the%20songs%20that%20were%20picturised%20on%20him%20composed%20by%20S.D.%20Burman%20as%20these%20define%20Dev%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201950s%2C%20Dev%20Anand%20was%20in%20several%20films%20which%20define%20the%20style%20of%20%E2%80%98Bombay%20Noir%E2%80%99%2C%20giving%20a%20certain%20grittiness%20in%20the%20depiction%20of%20the%20underworld%20or%20low%20life%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Bombay%2C%20mostly%20at%20night%2C%20which%20nevertheless%20looks%20glamorous%20and%20alluring%20with%20dangerous%20and%20seductive%20women%2C%20often%20vamps%20performing%20in%20nightclubs.%20These%20crime%20thrillers%20often%20feature%20cars%2C%20guns%2C%20phones%20such%20as%20in%20the%20fabulous%20opening%20sequences%20of%20%3Cem%3ECID%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Most%20of%20these%20films%20were%20made%20with%20Navketan%20Films.%20My%20favourites%20include%20those%20directed%20by%20Chetan%20Anand%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMRWDCx_z-Ns%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETaxi%20Driver%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%201954)%2C%20Guru%20Dutt%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXrUsbx8XkHw%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBaazi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%201951)%2C%20Vijay%20Anand%20(%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP_Thh7SiHlY%5C%22%3EKala%20Bazaar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%201960)%20and%20Raj%20Khosla%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcQ_tCziP04s%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKala%20Pani%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%201958).%20Dev%20Anand%20also%20acted%20in%20Guru%20Dutt%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuOjeDbhbyfw%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJaal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1952)%20and%20Raj%20Khosla%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DP-WFJ5-Ug3k%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECID%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1956)%2C%20both%20produced%20by%20Guru%20Dutt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20%3Cem%3ECID%3C%2Fem%3E%20whose%20music%20was%20composed%20by%20O.P.%20Nayyar%2C%20the%20others%20are%20all%20by%20S.D.%20Burman%20and%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20loved%20songs%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Hindi%20film%20music.%20While%20Hemant%20Kumar%20sang%20what%20Yash%20Chopra%20called%20his%20favourite%20film%20songs%2C%20Sahir%20Ludhianvi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-6I1JahC6VE%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EYeh%20raat%2C%20yeh%20chandni%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20in%20%3Cem%3EJaal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20songs%20picturised%20on%20Dev%20Anand%20were%20mostly%20sung%20by%20Mohammed%20Rafi%20and%20Kishore%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-6I1JahC6VE%3Fsi%3Dbr22CZH_0i1-qsez%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Dev%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20songs%20were%20a%20hugely%20important%20part%20of%20his%20star%20persona%2C%20huge%20popularity%20and%20great%20legacy%2C%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20%E2%80%98a%20voice%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20way%20that%20Raj%20Kapoor%20had%20Mukesh%20or%20Amitabh%20had%20Kishore%20Kumar%20but%20is%20closely%20associated%20with%20both%20Rafi%20and%20Kishore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20choose%20between%20Rafi%20and%20Kishore.%20It%20would%20be%20absurd%20as%20they%20are%20so%20different.%20S.D.%20Burman%20also%20used%20them%20both%20for%20great%20songs.%C2%A0%20However%2C%20S.D.%20Burman%20said%20he%20thought%20Dev%20Anand%20and%20Kishore%20were%20a%20perfect%20match.%20In%20Anirudh%20Bhattacharjee%20and%20Parthiv%20Dhar%E2%80%99s%20recent%20book%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FKishore-Kumar-Biography-Anirudha-Bhattacharjee%2Fdp%2F9356291713%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3EKishore%20Kumar%3A%20The%20Ultimate%20Biography%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20S.D.%20Burman%20is%20quoted%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%98Kishore%5B%E2%80%98s%5D%E2%80%A6voice%20was%20born%20for%20the%20actor%E2%80%A6When%20I%20composed%20for%20Dev%2C%20I%20categorically%20tried%20to%20induct%20Kishore.%20Given%20his%20impulsive%20nature%E2%80%A6%5Bhe%5D%20would%20not%20be%20available%20for%20days%20together.%20I%20used%20to%20resort%20to%20Rafi%E2%80%99s%20voice.%E2%80%99%20(p.%20321-2).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDev%20Anand%20and%20Kishore%20also%20had%20a%20great%20rapport%20and%20much%20mutual%20admiration.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20it%20was%20so%20great%20after%20%3Cem%3EBaazi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20Kishore%20had%20a%20picture%20of%20Dev%20Anand%20on%20his%20wall%20(p.%20165).%20Dev%20Anand%20said%20that%20he%20would%20pay%20Kishore%20as%20much%20as%20he%20received%20for%20a%20film%20as%20he%20found%20that%20Kishore%20could%20get%20his%20style%20just%20right%20(p.189).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fthe-guide-hindi-english-versions%5C%22%3EThe%20Hindi%20%E2%80%98Guide%E2%80%99%20Is%20Audience-Adoring%2C%20but%20Its%20English%20Version%20Is%20Audience-Ignoring%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDev%20Anand%2C%20S.D.%20Burman%20and%20Kishore%20worked%20together%20on%20over%20100%20songs.%20Kishore%20sang%20many%20more%20songs%20for%20Rajesh%20Khanna%20and%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20but%20they%20were%20usually%20with%20R.D.%20Burman.%20I%20suggest%20that%20the%20romantic%20persona%20of%20Dev%20Anand%20was%20the%20source%20of%20the%20middle%20class%20romantic%20hero%20that%20Rajesh%20Khanna%20took%20in%20the%20late%201960s%2C%20another%20non-dancing%20hero%20with%20much%20imitated%20facial%20expressions%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20period%20of%20Dev%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20work%20that%20I%20liked%20most.%20Although%20I%20watched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8n0qIz1oBmg%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EJoshila%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(1973)%20when%20I%20was%20working%20on%20Yash%20Chopra%2C%20it%20is%20not%20memorable.%20Dev%20Anand%E2%80%99s%20directorial%20film%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIAnJk1lQUqQ%5C%22%3E%20%3Cem%3EPrem%20Pujari%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(1970)%20had%20some%20massive%20hits%20by%20S.D.%20Burman%20sung%20by%20Kishore%3A%20%E2%80%99%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlZ4hoCYKKM4%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShokhiyon%20mein%20ghol%3C%2Fem%3Ea%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20and%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4CwFFWleNNA%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPhoolon%20ke%20rang%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99.%20The%20last%20Dev%20Anand%20film%20I%20saw%20was%20the%20hippy%20classic%2C%20%3Cem%3EHare%20Rama%20Hare%20Krishna%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1971).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbove%20all%20I%20think%20of%20Dev%20Anand%20from%20the%201950s%20and%201960s%2C%20when%20he%20gave%20great%20performances%20in%20outstanding%20films%20with%20memorable%20songs%20by%20S.D.%20Burman%2C%20sung%20by%20Kishore%20Kumar.%20This%20is%20how%20I%20will%20always%20remember%20and%20cherish%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHappy%20Birthday%2C%20Dev%20Saab.%20Stay%20forever%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Frachel%5C%22%3ERachel%20Dwyer%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20professor%20emerita%20of%20Indian%20culture%20and%20cinema%20at%20SOAS%2C%20University%20of%20London.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695645058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25164355%2Fimage-1352.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fdev-anand-was-a-stylish-icon-of-hindi-cinema-who-reflected-indian-modernity%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20tribute%20to%20the%20star%20who%20gave%20us%20some%20great%20films%2C%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20his%20100th%20anniversary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fdev-anand-was-a-stylish-icon-of-hindi-cinema-who-reflected-indian-modernity%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20Bandh%20Tomorrow%20Over%20Cauvery%20Water%20Release%20To%20Tamil%20Nadu%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20ongoing%20protests%20across%20Karnataka%20against%20releasing%20Cauvery%20river%20water%20to%20neighbouring%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20two%20bandhs%20have%20been%20called%20this%20week%20--%20in%20Bengaluru%20tomorrow%2C%20and%20statewide%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20for%20the%20Karnataka%20bandh%20on%20September%2029%20was%20made%20on%20Monday%2C%20under%20the%20banner%20'Kannada%20Okkuta'%20--%20led%20by%20Kannada%20activist%20Vatal%20Nagaraj%2C%20days%20after%20the%20'Karnataka%20Jala%20Samrakshana%20Samiti'%2C%20an%20umbrella%20outfit%20of%20farmers'%20associations%20and%20other%20organisations%20led%20by%20farmer%20leader%20Kuruburu%20Shanthakumar%20gave%20the%20call%20for%20Tuesday's%20Bengaluru%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20bandhs%20reflect%20the%20divide%20among%20the%20farmers%20and%20pro-Kannada%20organisations%2C%20and%20has%20also%20now%20led%20to%20a%20confusion%20about%20who%20is%20supporting%20the%20bandh%20on%20which%20day%2C%20and%20whether%20services%20will%20be%20available%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Shanthakumar%20has%20said%20that%20they%20will%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20Bengaluru%20bandh%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Vatal%20Nagaraj%2C%20who%20has%20called%20for%20a%20state%20bandh%20on%20Friday%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Kannada%20Okkuta%20is%20not%20supporting%20tomorrow's%20bandh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShanthakumar%20said%20they%20have%20received%20support%20from%20a%20number%20of%20organisations%20for%20their%20bandh%20call%20tomorrow%20and%20will%20go%20ahead%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20come%20in%20a%20protest%20to%20Bengaluru's%20Freedom%20Park%20and%20stage%20a%20demonstration%20there%20with%20our%20demands.%20The%20state%20government%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20will%20have%20to%20receive%20our%20memorandum.%20If%20there%20is%20no%20proper%20response%20to%20our%20protest%20from%20the%20government%2C%20we%20will%20decide%20on%20our%20further%20course%20of%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECalling%20for%20a%20peaceful%20bandh%2C%20he%20also%20appealed%20to%20the%20police%20to%20take%20adequate%20measures%20to%20ensure%20there%20are%20no%20untoward%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVatal%20Nagaraj%20said%20they%20had%20asked%20'Karnataka%20Jala%20Samrakshana%20Samiti'%20to%20postpone%20their%20bandh%20call%20and%20to%20observe%20it%20together%20with%20them%20on%20September%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20have%20called%20is%20Akhanda%20Karnataka%20bandh%20(entire%20Karnataka%20bandh)%20on%20September%2029.%20It%20will%20be%20observed%20across%20the%20state%20without%20leaving%20any%20district.%20Our%20fight%20is%20for%20entire%20Karnataka.%20Kannada%20Okkuta%20has%20organised%20more%20than%2050%20bandhs%20in%20the%20whole%20state%20so%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20as%20he%20questioned%20why%20the%20bandh%20was%20called%20by%20others%20only%20for%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ola-Uber%20Drivers'%20Association%20today%20said%20they%20would%20extend%20full%20support%20for%20the%20September%2029%20Karnataka%20bandh%20called%20by%20pro-Kannada%20organisations%20but%20will%20not%20support%20tomorrow's%20bandh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTomorrow%20our%20services%20will%20be%20normal.%20This%20decision%20was%20taken%20in%20a%20meeting%20held%20today%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20pro-Kannada%20and%20various%20organisations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20association%20in%20a%20statement%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20drivers%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20financial%20difficulties%20and%20they%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20they%20cannot%20afford%20to%20lose%20two%20days%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hotel%20Owner's%20Association%20too%20has%20decided%20to%20withdraw%20support%20for%20the%20bandh%20tomorrow%2C%20citing%20confusion%2C%20and%20said%20all%20hotels%20and%20restaurants%20will%20be%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20associations%20and%20unions%20operating%20autos%20and%20taxis%20have%20extended%20their%20complete%20support%20for%20tomorrow's%20bandh%20call%2C%20and%20KSRTC%20Staff%20and%20Workers'%20Federation%20too%20had%20asked%20Bengaluru%20Metropolitan%20Transport%20Corporation%20(BMTC)%20staff%20not%20to%20bring%20out%20any%20buses%20from%20depots%20from%20dawn%20to%20dusk%20(6%20am%20to%206%20pm).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMetro%20services%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20unaffected%20by%20the%20bandh%20call%20and%20would%20continue%20to%20function%20as%20usual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20private%20schools%20and%20colleges%20across%20the%20state%20have%20already%20declared%20a%20holiday%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Bengaluru%20bandh%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJD(S)%20leader%20H%20D%20Kumaraswamy%20said%20his%20party%20would%20support%20tomorrow's%20bandh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20asked%20my%20party%20workers%20to%20support%20the%20bandh.%20Our%20workers%20will%20support.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20chance%20for%20any%20untoward%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20D%20K%20Shivakumar%20also%20said%20that%20the%20people%20have%20the%20right%20to%20protest%20but%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20violence.%20Addressing%20media%20here%2C%20he%20said%2C%20protest%20is%20everyone's%20right%20in%20a%20democracy%20and%20it%20will%20not%20be%20curtailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20party%20people%20too%20called%20and%20spoke%20to%20me%20about%20the%20protest%2C%20I%20said%2C%20it's%20your%20right%20and%20protect%20it...but%20one%20has%20to%20understand%20about%20court%20orders%20before%20calling%20for%20protests%20or%20bandh%2C%20just%20giving%20such%20calls%20for%20media%20publicity%20is%20not%20right%2C%20as%20such%20calls%20may%20have%20legal%20repercussions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20keeping%20everything%20in%20mind%2C%20let%20them%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20public%20doesn't%20cooperate%2C%20the%20bandh%20will%20not%20have%20any%20value%2C%20said%20Shivakumar%2C%20citing%20alleged%20lack%20of%20consensus%20among%20the%20organisations%20on%20the%20bandh%20call%2C%20and%20two%20bandhs%20being%20called.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20will%20not%20interfere%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%20City%20police%20are%20taking%20all%20adequate%20security%20measures%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20untoward%20incident%20takes%20place%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695645000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fciqj2r28_bengaluru-protest-cauvery-1200_625x300_25_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengaluru-bandh-tomorrow-over-cauvery-water-release-to-tamil-nadu-4422082%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20ongoing%20protests%20across%20Karnataka%20against%20releasing%20Cauvery%20river%20water%20to%20neighbouring%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20two%20bandhs%20have%20been%20called%20this%20week%20--%20in%20Bengaluru%20tomorrow%2C%20and%20statewide%20on%20Fr