fore%20implementing%20the%20option%20of%20multiple%20entry%20and%20multiple%20exit%20(MEME)%20under%20the%20national%20education%20policy%20(NEP).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Education%2C%20headed%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Vivek%20Thakur%2C%20made%20the%20recommendation%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Feducation%2Fnational-education-policy-2020-multiple-entry-multiple-exit-option-may-not-work-well-for-india-house-panel%2Farticle67341734.ece%5C%22%3Egovernment%20faced%20significant%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20students%20and%20teachers%20on%20the%20provision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20panel%2C%20in%20a%20report%20titled%20%E2%80%98Implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%202020%20in%20Higher%20Education%E2%80%99%2C%20said%20Indian%20institutions%20were%20likely%20to%20face%20several%20issues%20in%20implementing%20this%20system.%20The%20report%20was%20tabled%20in%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20during%20the%20recently%20concluded%20special%20session%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Feducation%2Fnational-education-policy-2020-multiple-entry-multiple-exit-option-may-not-work-well-for-india-house-panel%2Farticle67341734.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20the%20panel%20said%20that%20while%20MEME%20has%20been%20successfully%20implemented%20in%20the%20West%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20execute%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20institutions%20allow%20MEME%2C%20it%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20the%20institutions%20to%20predict%20how%20many%20students%20would%20exit%20and%20how%20many%20would%20join%20midway.%20Since%20institutions%20would%20not%20know%20the%20in-%20and%20out-traffic%2C%20it%20will%20certainly%20disturb%20the%20pupil-teacher%20ratio%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fs