and%20inhabited%20by%20indigenous%20communities%20and%20required%20by%20large%20companies%E2%80%94required%20to%20build%20giant%20plants%20and%20the%20attendant%20mines%20to%20feed%20them%20ore.%20Still%20more%20land%20was%20then%20required%20to%20store%E2%80%94dump%2C%20really%E2%80%94the%20toxic%20waste%20products%20of%20the%20industrial%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20327px)%2085vw%2C%20327px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25092125%2FScreenshot-2023-09-25-at-9.21.04-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22327%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25092125%2FScreenshot-2023-09-25-at-9.21.04-AM.png%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25092125%2FScreenshot-2023-09-25-at-9.21.04-AM-186x300.png%20186w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25092125%2FScreenshot-2023-09-25-at-9.21.04-AM-634x1024.png%20634w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22528%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98After%20Messiah%3A%20What%20Comes%20When%20a%20Great%20Leader%20Goes%E2%80%99%2C%20Aakar%20Patel%2C%20Penguin%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20had%20laws%20under%20which%20it%20could%20arbitrarily%20seize%20private%20property%2C%20but%20this%20capture%20was%20couched%20as%20being%20fair%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20all.%20The%20first%20step%20of%20the%20acquisition%20was%20that%20those%20who%20owned%20the%20fields%20and%20mountains%20and%20streams%20were%20informed%20through%20gazettes%20in%20government%20offices%20that%20their%20property%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20taken%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20thirty%20days%20to%20file%20their%20objections%2C%20assuming%20they%20had%20knowledge%20of%20what%20was%20put%20on%20government%20noticeboards%2C%20any%20more%20than%20any%20other%20citizen%20has.%20After%20the%20objections%20had%20been%20filed%2C%20a%20meeting%E2%80%94called%20a%20%E2%80%98public%20consultation%E2%80%99%20but%20actually%20nothing%20of%20the%20sort%E2%80%94was%20held%20with%20those%20who%20did%20not%20consent.%20The%20company%20investing%20in%20the%20project%20also%20sent%20its%20own%20people%20there%2C%20and%20in%20the%20noisy%20and%20often%20violent%20chaos%20that%20ensued%2C%20not%20much%20was%20resolved.%20Local%20middlemen%20were%20hired%20to%20lure%20or%20bully%20those%20who%20objected%20or%20were%20refusing%20to%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20simultaneous%20process%20of%20taking%20over%20some%20land%20and%20then%20pressuring%20the%20rest%20to%20give%20more%20would%20begin.%20In%20time%2C%20the%20owners%20of%20adjoining%20lands%20would%20have%20less%20incentive%20to%20resist%20because%20the%20borders%20of%20their%20property%20would%20be%20encroached%20on%E2%80%94not%20just%20physically%20but%20also%20through%20the%20noise%20and%20the%20emissions%20and%20the%20waste%2C%20the%20poisoned%20waters%20and%20the%20ash%20settling%20on%20their%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20ability%20to%20negotiate%20the%20terms%20of%20their%20fate%2C%20and%20that%20of%20their%20children%20and%20of%20their%20ancestral%20inheritance%2C%20began%20to%20diminish%20from%20the%20moment%20someone%20somewhere%20circled%20their%20property%20on%20a%20map.%20The%20state%20here%20was%20an%20opponent%2C%20even%20an%20adversary%2C%20when%20it%20felt%20that%20its%20interests%20clashed%20with%20those%20of%20the%20communities.%20The%20agents%20of%20the%20state%2C%20the%20lower%20bureaucracy%2C%20the%20police%2C%20the%20district%20magistrates%2C%20had%20no%20incentive%20to%20protect%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20communities%20and%20of%20individuals.%20They%20had%20their%20orders%20and%20targets%20to%20achieve%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20other%20side%2C%20the%20corporate%20firms%20and%20their%20owners%2C%20that%20had%20leverage%20over%20them%2C%20far%20more%20than%20the%20protesting%20individuals%20who%20were%20seen%20merely%20as%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20mineral%20wealth%20lay%20not%20under%20the%20cities%20but%20in%20the%20deep%20heart%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20things%20that%20went%20on%20and%20concerned%20the%20people%20of%20these%20parts%20did%20not%20occupy%20the%20minds%20of%20those%20in%20the%20cities.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20to%20vacate%20their%20flats%20so%20that%20the%20ground%20below%20could%20be%20dug%20up%20for%20coal%20or%20bauxite.%20They%20often%20had%20the%20power%20to%20veto%20what%20could%20and%20could%20not%20happen%20outside%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20would%20they%20have%20dealt%20with%20the%20knowledge%20that%20in%20parts%20of%20their%20own%20country%2C%20schools%20were%20closed%20for%20much%20of%20the%20day%20because%20dynamite%20was%20used%20to%20open%20up%20mines%2C%20shaking%20the%20lands%20around%3F%20Most%20of%20them%2C%20of%20course%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20known%20that%20such%20year-round%20seismic%20Diwalis%20existed.%20They%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20seen%20an%20%E2%80%98ash%20pond%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20salubrious-sounding%20space%20that%20was%20actually%20mounds%20and%20hillocks%20of%20black%20waste%20as%20far%20as%20the%20eye%20could%20see.%20This%20Mordor%2C%20so%20alien%20and%20unreal%2C%20terrifying%20to%20those%20who%20encountered%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20city%20dwellers%20were%20unfamiliar%20with%20it%20in%20reality%2C%20though%20perhaps%20not%20in%20fiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fstate-level-changes-land-laws-return-land-grabbing-developments-name%5C%22%3EIn%20State-Level%20Changes%20to%20Land%20Laws%2C%20a%20Return%20to%20Land%20Grabbing%20in%20Development%E2%80%99s%20Name%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20lawyers%20knew.%20Particularly%20those%2C%20like%20Mira%2C%20who%20had%20chosen%20to%20work%20outside%20the%20cities.%20The%20state%20had%20laws%20that%20gave%20them%20just%20enough%20space%20to%20engage%20with%20it%2C%20laws%20that%20gave%20the%20people%20who%20owned%20those%20jungles%20and%20hills%20and%20valleys%20the%20notional%20right%20to%20safeguards.%20What%20was%20on%20paper%2C%20however%2C%20was%20subject%20to%20interpretation%2C%20and%20what%20was%20subjective%20was%20determined%20by%20those%20who%20held%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20law%20required%20the%20state%20to%20act%20when%20these%20safeguards%20were%20violated%2C%20it%20ignored%2C%20avoided%2C%20shirked%20and%20refused.%20What%20it%20was%20focused%20on%20was%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%E2%80%93%20the%20development%20of%20roads%20on%20which%20to%20ferry%20the%20wealth%20to%20the%20cities%2C%20and%20of%20paramilitary%20camps%20to%20pacify%20the%20locals.%20The%20business%20press%20reported%20the%20rising%20volumes%20of%20mine%20ore%2C%20as%20if%20it%20represented%20progress.%20The%20state%20and%20its%20ministries%20put%20out%20data%20on%20extraction%2C%20as%20if%20plundering%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20property%20and%20devastating%20the%20countryside%20was%20some%20signal%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20wealth%20of%20those%20fattened%20on%20extractives%20was%20legitimized%20on%20billionaires%E2%80%99%20lists.%20Those%20in%20elected%20office%20held%20up%20these%20numbers%2C%20in%20millions%20of%20tonnes%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20as%20an%20indicator%20of%20their%20leadership.%20The%20locals%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20were%20accused%20of%20holding%20up%20development%2C%20and%20those%20standing%20with%20them%20in%20support%20were%20called%20enemies%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20slandering%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20those%20affected%20would%20stop%20trying%2C%20and%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20The%20abusive%20words%20were%20not%20the%20problem%3B%20the%20problem%20was%20the%20injustice%20of%20what%20was%20happening%20and%20would%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20the%20cause%20of%20such%20people%20that%20the%20collective%20had%20thrown%20itself.%20Having%20taken%20themselves%20to%20the%20areas%20where%20this%20kind%20of%20land-grab%20was%20happening%2C%20they%20knew%20where%20the%20interventions%20were%20required%3A%20when%20responding%20to%20the%20gazette%2C%20at%20the%20public%20consultation%2C%20at%20the%20point%20of%20helping%20organize%20the%20communities%20and%20putting%20them%20in%20touch%20with%20one%20another%2C%20at%20the%20point%20of%20informing%20them%20of%20their%20legal%20rights%20and%20safeguards%2C%20and%20at%20the%20police%20station%20to%20file%20complaints.%20This%20was%20the%20work%20the%20lawyers%20at%20the%20collective%20did.%20The%20firm%20could%20not%2C%20and%20did%20not%2C%20pay%20itself%20and%20its%20lawyers%20what%20they%20might%20have%20been%20able%20to%20make%20in%20another%20place%20or%20working%20for%20another%20cause.%20But%20it%20was%20work%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20and%20it%20easily%20and%20continually%20attracted%20outstanding%20talent%20in%20the%20numbers%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695623447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F25093507%2F9623884002_829083ac6a_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faakar-patel-after-messiah-book-land-law-seize%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20mineral%20wealth%20lay%20not%20under%20the%20cities%20but%20in%20the%20deep%20heart%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20things%20that%20went%20on%20and%20concerned%20the%20people%20of%20these%20parts%20did%20not%20occupy%20the%20minds%20of%20those%20in%20the%20cities.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faakar-patel-after-messiah-book-land-law-seize%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22