%20being%20in%20nature%20and%20among%20wildlife%20makes%20her%20job%20more%20fun%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsonali-ghosh-3-1695301158-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330490%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESonali%20says%20that%20being%20in%20nature%20and%20among%20wildlife%20makes%20her%20job%20more%20fun.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Sonali%20Ghosh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Sonali%20says%2C%20she%20did%20not%20care%20about%20opinions%20and%20continued%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20work%2C%20keeping%20her%20work%20above%20everything%20else.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMother%20to%20a%20young%20girl%2C%20she%20often%20had%20to%20spend%20months%20without%20her%20child%20away%20from%20home.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20such%20cases%2C%20a%20strong%20family%20relationship%20is%20essential%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20workload%20could%20be%20such%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20neglecting%20even%20my%20health%20in%20many%20instances%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20family%20always%20came%20to%20her%20rescue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeing%20chased%20by%20rhinos%20to%20climbing%20trees%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20the%20field%20director%20at%20Kaziranga%2C%20she%20has%20held%20several%20other%20titles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20DFO%20(Divisional%20Forest