lls%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20be%20wonderful%20if%20the%20cab%20driver%20could%20know%20which%20fuel%20station%20had%20a%20lesser%20waiting%20time%3F%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20%E2%80%98Nawgati%E2%80%99%20came%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%2020%20then%2C%20and%20in%20his%20third-year%20of%20engineering%2C%20Vaibhav%20thought%20that%20this%20problem%20must%20have%20been%20solved%20by%20someone.%20To%20his%20surprise%2C%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20solution%2C%20he%20started%20working%20on%20one%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20Aalaap%20Nair%20and%20Aryan%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20researched%20various%20pain%20points%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20customers%20and%20fuel%20stations.%20They%20then%20spoke%20to%20fuel%20providers%20and%20examined%20their%20in-house%20challenges%20and%20difficulties.%20After%20this%2C%20they%20built%20the%20technology%2C%20a%20queue%20management%20platform%2C%20which%20would%20help%20both%20fuel%20stations%20and%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20fuel%20companies%20improve%20efficiency%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20founders%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENawgati%20founders%20%E2%80%93%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20came%20up%20with%20two%20solutions%2C%20an%20app%20for%20consumers%2C%20and%20its%20flagship%20product%2C%20Aaveg%2C%20a%20B2B%20platform%2C%20for%20fuel%20companies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20improve%20compliance%2C%20achieve%20operational%20efficiency%2C%20monitor%20real-time%20congestion%2C%20and%20direct%20customers%20to%20less%20crowded%20stations%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAaveg%20is%20a%20single%20point%20of%20reference%20for%20fuel%20station%20owners%20to%20have%20complete%20oversight%20of%20transit%2C%20waiting%20and%20serving%20time%2C%20attendants%20deployed%2C%20and%20under%20or%20over-utilisation%20of%20resources.%20We%20help%20fuel%20companies%20and%2For%20dealers%20with%20congestion%20management%2C%20compliance%20monitoring%2C%20and%20automating%20forecourt%20operations%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20scale%20up%20or%20scale%20down%20operations%20at%20any%20outlet%20and%20make%20decisions%20backed%20by%20data%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aryan%2C%20co-founder%20and%20CTO%20at%20Nawgati.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Aaveg%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20Sanskrit%20for%20impulse%2C%20is%20built%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296093%2Fcouple-converts-tempo-traveller-into-caravan-to-travel-van-life-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplug-and-play%3C%2Fa%3E%20framework%20and%20aims%20to%20provide%20fuel%20companies%20%E2%80%98data%20within%20an%20impulse%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E