3E4.%20Chemeen%20Pada%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shrimp%20pickle%2C%20a%20staple%20in%20Tanya%E2%80%99s%20household%2C%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20Portuguese%20tradition%20of%20pickling%20meats%20in%20vinegar.%20In%20fact%2C%20as%20Tanya%20writes%2C%20vinegar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20foods%20brought%20to%20Kerala%20during%20the%20colonisation%20in%20the%2015th%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Portuguese%20used%20vinegar%20extensively%20in%20their%20food%3B%20especially%20to%20preserve%20salted%20meats%20with%20paprika%20and%20garlic%20which%20were%20stored%20in%20large%20barrels%20during%20their%20voyages%20in%20ships%20to%20lands%20afar.%20This%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20quick%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324582%2Fshashikala-sanadhya-gives-indian-food-cooking-lessons-for-foreign-tourists-in-udaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esavouring%20dish%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20fried%20in%20oil%2C%20close%20to%20the%20meat%20pickle%20famously%20relished%20in%20Kerala%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20Kazhal%20Kothiyathu%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Latin%20Catholic%20minced%20liver%20fry%20recipe%20prepared%20by%20Tanya%E2%80%99s%20grandmother%20differs%20from%20other%20community%20recipes%20in%20terms%20of%20preparation.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20unusual%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tanya%2C%20who%20noticed%20how%20cooking%20styles%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322885%2Fkarnataka-shivaranjini-started-suggi-oota-south-indian-restaurant-in-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecipes%3C%2Fa%3E%20differed%20across%20catholic%20communities%20even%20within%20Kerala%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20choppers%20were%20not%20available%2C%20quick%20and%20constant%20chopping%20of%20the%20meat%20on%20a%20large%20wooden%20boar